g.title: j4064530753
g.text: wait, u taught Arthur how emoticons work?? THANK U

g.title: j3399540335
g.text: Yep, sat him down and explained the whole thing. He was so confused at first.

g.title: j3538909194
g.text: Just doing my part to keep the team literate.

g.title: j3703420516
g.text: You know, I can tell when you're upset.

g.title: j263536460
g.text: gosh I am so grateful! now he won’t think I'm challenging him to a duel every time I use “;)”

g.title: j2919355680
g.text: Haha please tell me that didn't really happen.

g.title: j2114679923
g.text: Oh Arthur... I guess nobody's perfect.

g.title: j466680115
g.text: good guess! I use that one a lot because it's so darn versatile, but it's not my fave

g.title: j3515493670
g.text: of course u can. we manic pixie dream girls wear our hearts on her sleeves

g.title: j3340132688
g.text: ding ding ding! we have a winner! how did u know?

g.title: j1378192968
g.text: Okay, I admit that calling your interest in me a "manic pixie dream girl act" was inconsiderate.

g.title: j1823509568
g.text: When I said that manic pixie thing, I only meant you don't have to put on an act for me.

g.title: j1819717215
g.text: I can't believe he actually apologized! all thx to u <3

g.title: j1705504344
g.text: oooo not quite but that one's up there!

g.title: j990629355
g.text: u get one more guess, but only cuz ur so cool

g.title: j4004394101
g.text: It's just the right mix of cute and witty.

g.title: j1218163699
g.text: at least u found it "cute and all"

g.title: j2356011241
g.text: wut makes u think its an act?

g.title: j4265299208
g.text: I live to serve, my lady.

g.title: j2984508406
g.text: It was the least I could do.

g.title: j800308556
g.text: Well, it was. You're cute. I mean unbelievably cute. I just find it hard to believe.

g.title: j1738778184
g.text: Nobody's actually bubbly and fun all the time.

g.title: j2461249573
g.text: I can see a deeper side to you, Aoi. You're tough. You're more than pop songs and emoticons.

g.title: j2907863738
g.text: u srsly might have just saved us from a lifetime of confusion

g.title: j1583361797
g.text: Well, now I know something you love, and I'll never forget it.

g.title: j1887913210
g.text: how am I supposed to receive that?

g.title: j2922092338
g.text: nobody's serious and boring all the time either

g.title: j257619842
g.text: it concerns me that u don't think depth, toughness, pop songs, and emoticons can go together

g.title: j4047090669
g.text: Glad I could help. So, of all the emoticons you've memorized, which is your favorite?

g.title: j1920675390
g.text: Hey, Arthur was missing out. Your emoticons are fun. Which is your favorite?

g.title: j226526492
g.text: Ooooh I can see why that would be your favorite.

g.title: j500912413
g.text: It makes you happy that I've given up?

g.title: j578973635
g.text: I knew it was that one.

g.title: j694372091
g.text: yet there's always more to uncover ;)

g.title: j43490378
g.text: Listen, I think you're amazing. I said that manic pixie crap because I doubt myself, not you. I'm sorry.

g.title: j2731378904
g.text: I'd like it if you received it as me thinking you're awesome.

g.title: j526031614
g.text: at least nobody I want to be around

g.title: j1591523422
g.text: that might be true for u, but that doesn't mean it's true for everyone

g.title: j1760423535
g.text: whatever I did to deserve u in my life, I hope no time-travelling mischief-maker ever goes back and changes it <3

g.title: j1541339627
g.text: I get that u have bad days. who doesn't, right?

g.title: j2966962124
g.text: I just don't buy that making people happy is your whole reason for being. There's gotta be more to you than that.

g.title: j562197005
g.text: Okay, fair point. You're right. What I said was more about me than you.

g.title: j2686531661
g.text: LOL I never should have doubted u

g.title: j3637009015
g.text: but u can't just take it out on me cuz I seem "cute" enough to put up with it

g.title: j34945461
g.text: maybe u just haven't been paying attention

g.title: j2607529359
g.text: I was revealing my fave emoticon!

g.title: j2009372005
g.text: You're right. You deserve better. I'll earn back your faith in me. That's a promise.

g.title: j3093522373
g.text: So you want me to just hide it from you when I've had a bad day?

g.title: j1418704922
g.text: I get that u have bad days. who doesn't, right?

g.title: j3404231276
g.text: ur introspection is awfully charming, I admit

g.title: j2398562505
g.text: u know that's not what I mean

g.title: j2458245832
g.text: but u can't just take it out on me cuz I seem nice enough to put up with it

g.title: j2308576316
g.text: I do like the sound of that promise...

g.title: j973875167
g.text: Okay it was a bad joke.

g.title: j2214279621
g.text: ok let's put this behind us

g.title: j1501602514
g.text: If that's what you'd like, it's what I'd like.

g.title: j3613880366
g.text: Okay maybe I'm being a little... avoidant.

g.title: j1000147373
g.text: look I'm gonna put this behind us, ok?

g.title: j2935314052
g.text: (in case you don't know, ttyl means "talk to you later")
